title: Strawberry Cannoli By BAMS
description: Strawberry Cannoli by Bam’s Cannoli is a delectable e liquid that tastes like a cannoli filled with fresh sugary strawberry icing. Anyone looking for a dessert flavored e juice, Strawberry Cannoli is exactly what you need. Upon inhaling, you are hit with the sweet and smooth strawberry icing flavor. The slight pastry undertone flavoring complements the smooth strawberry inhale and really brings this whole dessert vape experience together into one.Flavor Profile: Strawberry, Cannoli, Whipped CreamVG/PG: 80/20Nicotine Level: 0MG, 3MG, 6MGBottle Size: 100ML
